com.emc.esu.api.rest
Class UploadHelper

java.lang.Object
  com.emc.esu.api.rest.UploadHelper

public class UploadHelper
extends Object

Helper class to create and update objects. For large transfers, the content generally needs to be transferred to the server in smaller chunks. This class reads data from either a file or a stream and incrementally uploads it to the server. The class also supports the registering of a listener object to report status back to the calling application.
